rComments: Loves the sound of his own voice. Didn't learn much from his class at all, just meh.

he's okay. not the best I ever had. his teaching is not my cup of tea. doesnt teach you much new and sometimes makes you feel stupid for asking certain questions but i guess that's his thing. he does know his stuff though. I got an A in the class

Julius is a very engaging and clear lecturer. His class was thoroughly enjoyable. He was also a VERY fair marker. If you put in the work and paid attention during lectures, you're golden. The test and exam were so fair, I almost thought it was a joke. He didn't try to trick you at all. It was all a good test of your knowledge. I ended up with a 90
